        {
            "title": "荷姆茲危機引發油市大亂！不只現貨比期貨貴 傳統原油交易模式也崩盤",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mQUBPpTeX2g9QxblOSp0bA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f61cb7ac8276b1f526af952fa1ef190f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8D%B7%E5%A7%86%E8%8C%B2%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E6%B2%B9%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%82-%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AA%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8%E6%AF%94%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E8%B2%B4-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%9F%E5%B4%A9%E7%9B%A4-170002574.html",
